## Adaptation Mechanisms

### Temperature Calibration
- Adjusts warmth factors based on user feedback
- Learns user's temperature comfort zone
- Updates item properties for future suggestions

### Style Learning
- Tracks item combinations that work well together
- Updates cohesion scores based on user feedback
- Improves style matching over time

### Preference Evolution
- Updates item preference scores
- Considers recency of wear
- Adapts to user's style preferences

